{"tid":941643,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"改詞試水溫：「偏偏捉不到 開始跟你緣份變老 」原陳奕迅〈葡萄成熟時〉","createTime":"2018-12-15T03:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T10:46:37.000Z","uid":206050,"like":7,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a35b0aa54a8d73f1bc47e1794b8d9873b12285","tid":941643,"uid":206050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都幾矛盾 明知兒登低質唔應該po過黎 但又貪佢人多 想推廣自己作品/搵人演唱<br />\n點知一禁入創意台改詞分頁 果然一大堆垃圾教會膠歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d改詞高手全部都唔見曬 卒之諗黎諗去<br />\n惟有特登po錯台 黎校園台先試吓水溫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過生為高登人 死作高登魂 循例要宣傳返高質討論區：高登同埋高登音樂台<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2F&d=N%2BZHHA5PkGUt1wp1OvUEY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=33abe1ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/</a>(驚有d蛋蛋後唔知咩黎 我連link都比埋你)<br />\n本改詞高登原post：<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=6996153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DEP%26message%3D6996153&d=N%2BZHHA5PkGUt1wp1OvUEY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=68562b6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=6996153</a><br />\n高登音樂台Home page：<a href=\"http://hkgoldenmusic.com/?fbclid=IwAR3OSS0Y17WPoNswOJrqZoGVpXzQpWaNH0QJUtDbNO6u4y5dyIOgR3iF0H0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgoldenmusic.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3OSS0Y17WPoNswOJrqZoGVpXzQpWaNH0QJUtDbNO6u4y5dyIOgR3iF0H0&d=N%2BZHHA5PkGUt1wp1OvUEY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=935e71e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkgoldenmusic.com/?fbclid=IwAR3OSS0Y17WPoNswOJrqZoGVpXzQpWaNH0QJUtDbNO6u4y5dyIOgR3iF0H0</a><br />\n高登音樂台Facebook page：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgoldenmusic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgoldenmusic%2F&d=N%2BZHHA5PkGUt1wp1OvUEY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4e988709\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgoldenmusic/</a><br />\n高登音樂台Youtube channel：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-PbFMH4uhmqO71Gyxr5A-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC-PbFMH4uhmqO71Gyxr5A-g&d=N%2BZHHA5PkGUt1wp1OvUEY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2e5da45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-PbFMH4uhmqO71Gyxr5A-g</a><br />\n<br />\n以下入正題<br />\n<br />\n改詞〈曾經的邂逅〉 是撚旦取名<br />\n<br />\n原演唱：陳奕迅〈葡萄成熟時〉 <br />\n原填詞：黃偉文 <br />\n原作曲：Vincent Chow/Anfernee Cheung <br />\n原編曲：Adrian Chan <br />\n原監製：Alvin Leong <br />\n<br />\n偏偏都不夠 怎麼將你緣份變厚 <br />\n青蔥的優游 像你別去不回頭 不回眸 <br />\n與你再相見 可會再牽手 <br />\n<br />\n真心早生鏽 今天跟你如像棄友 <br />\n孤單的憂愁 在我夢裡總凝留 <br />\n要追究 怪當初不佔有 <br />\n<br />\n但你神情迷離難看透 又與誰人同遊都協奏 <br />\n我放任後 卻造就 <br />\n讓某雙手 將你帶走 <br />\n<br />\n外貌 漸漸忘記彷彿似被易容 <br />\n回憶始終你的面紅 無悔恨有相擁 <br />\n某首 詩中 就像實現有你我的美夢 <br />\n若果我錯過 跟你那動人時空 <br />\n情真都會斷送 <br />\n<br />\n偏偏捉不到 開始跟你緣份變老 <br />\n相識的功勞 被你忘卻不能逃 怎能逃 <br />\n要你去廝守 總要說出口 <br />\n<br />\n心聲怎宣告 消失的你留下控訴 <br />\n當初的煎熬 是你令我感糊塗 <br />\n要追溯 怪不知你愛好 <br />\n<br />\n但你神情迷離難看透 又與誰人同遊都協奏 <br />\n我放任後 卻造就 <br />\n讓某雙手 將你帶走 <br />\n<br />\n外貌 漸漸忘記彷彿似被易容 <br />\n回憶始終你的面紅 無悔恨有相擁 <br />\n某首 詩中 就像實現有你我的美夢 <br />\n若果我錯過 跟你那動人時空 <br />\n情真都會斷送 <br />\n<br />\n苦戀 可惜今天亦變了愛妒 像遷怒 <br />\nWoo woo yeah yeah <br />\n今天 經已成為被告 難修補 <br />\nWoo woo woo <br />\n<br />\n熱鬧 慢慢逝去開出一道裂縫 <br />\n難得等到你的共融 留愛在我心中 <br />\n會否 鬧哄 就像現實對你我的戲弄 <br />\n若果已錯過 只盼未來時空 <br />\n仍可將你目送 <br />\n<br />\n曾經的邂逅 變到沒有"},{"pid":"839e738c05dd516020aefd193091f59458744140","tid":941643,"uid":81879,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"睇到副歌覺得怪怪地"},{"pid":"4fcf711e5826cde82485a098f4e97fe1b7653008","tid":941643,"uid":152701,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"咁嘅文筆同用詞<br />\n不如讀好啲大學先再出來顯柒啦<br />\n好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" cl